== 系統新增功能 ==

=== 接續互通 ===
iOS 8首度引入[[接續互通|接續互通]]功能體系，能不間斷的銜接[[蘋果裝置|蘋果裝置]]的作業。接續互通包括Handoff功能，能透過[[无线网络|無線網路]]或[[行動數據|行動數據]]在不同裝置間同步應用程式作業。在切換應用程式時，iOS 8会自动在多工處理界面上显示出用户近期在其它裝置上使用的應用程式，以便用户開啟應用程式继续作業<ref name=":7" /><ref name="iOS features">{{cite web|url=http://www.techtomorrow.in/ios8|title=ios 8|accessdate=2014-08-03|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20140808063418/http://www.techtomorrow.in/ios8|archivedate=2014-08-08|first1=ios|website=www.techtomorrow.in|deadurl=yes}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.apple.com/ios/ios8/continuity/|title=存档副本|accessdate=2014-09-09|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20140908015147/http://www.apple.com/ios/ios8/continuity/|archivedate=2014-09-08|deadurl=yes}}</ref>；通用剪貼板功能，能在不同裝置間同步[[复制|拷貝]]的文字、圖片或其他內容<ref name=":7" /><ref name="iOS features" /><ref name="Continuity2">{{cite web|url=http://appleinsider.com/articles/14/09/17/how-to-use-ios-8-continuity-between-your-iphone-ipad-for-calls-texts-apps-more|title=How to use iOS 8 Continuity between your iPhone & iPad for calls, texts, apps & more|accessdate=2016-12-22|date=2014-09-17|last=Hughes|first=Neil|website=AppleInsider|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20161222221655/http://appleinsider.com/articles/14/09/17/how-to-use-ios-8-continuity-between-your-iphone-ipad-for-calls-texts-apps-more|archive-date=2016-12-22|dead-url=no}}</ref>；行動網路通話功能，在同一環境下能使用[[Macintosh|Mac]]或[[iPad|iPad]]接聽、撥打電話<ref name=":7" /><ref name=":8" /><ref name="Continuity3">{{cite web|url=http://appleinsider.com/articles/14/09/17/how-to-use-ios-8-continuity-between-your-iphone-ipad-for-calls-texts-apps-more|title=How to use iOS 8 Continuity between your iPhone & iPad for calls, texts, apps & more|accessdate=2016-12-22|date=2014-09-17|last=Hughes|first=Neil|website=AppleInsider|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20161222221655/http://appleinsider.com/articles/14/09/17/how-to-use-ios-8-continuity-between-your-iphone-ipad-for-calls-texts-apps-more|archive-date=2016-12-22|dead-url=no}}</ref>；及Instant Hotspot功能，能透過Mac開啟iPhone[[热点_(Wi-Fi)|熱點]]<ref name=":7" /><ref name=":8" /><ref name="Continuity4">{{cite web|url=http://appleinsider.com/articles/14/09/17/how-to-use-ios-8-continuity-between-your-iphone-ipad-for-calls-texts-apps-more|title=How to use iOS 8 Continuity between your iPhone & iPad for calls, texts, apps & more|accessdate=2016-12-22|date=2014-09-17|last=Hughes|first=Neil|website=AppleInsider|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20161222221655/http://appleinsider.com/articles/14/09/17/how-to-use-ios-8-continuity-between-your-iphone-ipad-for-calls-texts-apps-more|archive-date=2016-12-22|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

由於軟體因素，接續互通只支援搭载iOS 8和[[OS_X_Yosemite|OS X Yosemite]]以上版本系统的裝置<ref name=":7" /><ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.cnet.com/news/apples-new-hand-off-brings-proximity-awareness/|title=Apple's Handoff brings proximity awareness to your devices|accessdate=2016-12-22|date=2014-06-02|last=Whitney|first=Lance|publisher=[[CBS_Interactive|CBS Interactive]]|website=[[CNET|CNET]]|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20161222155309/https://www.cnet.com/news/apples-new-hand-off-brings-proximity-awareness/|archive-date=2016-12-22|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.theverge.com/2014/10/16/6978157/mac-os-x-yosemite-release-mac-app-store-october-16th|title=OS X Yosemite will be available today from the Mac App Store|accessdate=2016-12-22|date=2014-10-16|last=Kastrenakes|first=Jacob|publisher=[[Vox_Media|Vox Media]]|website=[[The_Verge|The Verge]]|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20161231013032/http://www.theverge.com/2014/10/16/6978157/mac-os-x-yosemite-release-mac-app-store-october-16th/|archive-date=2016-12-31|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref name="Continuity">{{cite web|url=http://appleinsider.com/articles/14/09/17/how-to-use-ios-8-continuity-between-your-iphone-ipad-for-calls-texts-apps-more|title=How to use iOS 8 Continuity between your iPhone & iPad for calls, texts, apps & more|accessdate=2016-12-22|date=2014-09-17|last=Hughes|first=Neil|website=AppleInsider|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20161222221655/http://appleinsider.com/articles/14/09/17/how-to-use-ios-8-continuity-between-your-iphone-ipad-for-calls-texts-apps-more|archive-date=2016-12-22|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

