在iOS 8中，Spotlight進一步与網路服务整合，用户可以於搜尋欄中直接搜尋[[维基百科|维基百科]]、即時新聞、安裝在裝置上的應用程式、附近地点及[[iTunes_Store|iTunes Store]]媒體內容等<ref>{{cite web|url=http://bgr.com/2014/06/03/yosemite-and-ios-8-spotlight-search-features/|title=Here’s one major new Yosemite and iOS 8 feature that got overlooked|accessdate=2016-12-22|date=2014-06-03|last=Smith|first=Chris|publisher=[[Penske_Media_Corporation|Penske Media Corporation]]|website=[[Boy_Genius_Report|BGR]]|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170426211210/http://bgr.com/2014/06/03/yosemite-and-ios-8-spotlight-search-features/|archive-date=2017-04-26|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|url=https://9to5mac.com/2014/06/02/hands-on-with-spotlight-suggestions-in-ios-8-video/|title=Hands-on with Spotlight Suggestions in iOS 8 (Video)|accessdate=2016-12-22|date=2014-06-02|last=Esposito|first=Dom|website=9to5Mac|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20161222153827/https://9to5mac.com/2014/06/02/hands-on-with-spotlight-suggestions-in-ios-8-video/|archive-date=2016-12-22|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

=== 通知中心 ===
{{Main|通知 (iOS)}}
iOS 8的通知中心經過了重新設計，新增了[[Widget|小工具]]功能。第三方應用程式可開發附屬小工具，並由用戶加入通知中心。小工具不必透過應用程式即可顯示部分資訊，例如[[ESPN|ESPN]]運動比賽分數或[[eBay|eBay]]的競標資訊等。用户可以自由添加、移除小工具並排列次序<ref name=":6" /><ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.macworld.com/article/2686117/get-to-know-ios-8-customize-your-notification-center-with-handy-new-widgets.html|title=Get to know iOS 8: Customize your Notification Center with handy new widgets|accessdate=2016-12-22|date=2014-09-19|last=Walter|first=Derek|publisher=[[International_Data_Group|International Data Group]]|website=[[Macworld|Macworld]]|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20161222152655/http://www.macworld.com/article/2686117/get-to-know-ios-8-customize-your-notification-center-with-handy-new-widgets.html|archive-date=2016-12-22|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.macworld.co.uk/how-to/iosapps/ios-notification-centre-tips-3529660/|title=How to use iOS 8 Notification Centre|accessdate=2016-12-22|date=2014-11-26|last=Paris|first=Steve|publisher=[[International_Data_Group|International Data Group]]|website=[[Macworld|Macworld]]|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20161207040805/http://www.macworld.co.uk/how-to/iosapps/ios-notification-centre-tips-3529660/|archive-date=2016-12-07|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

出現於螢幕上緣的橫幅通知訊息現在加入了直接回覆功能，用戶可在不切換應用程式的情況下直接在通知橫幅中回覆簡訊、將電子郵件刪除或標示為已讀等<ref name=":6" />。

===鍵盤===
iOS 8首度引入全新QuickType鍵盤，可在輸入文字時即時顯示字詞的預測候選。iOS 8將自動學習使用者的輸入習慣和用詞風格，且能依據傳送對象產生不同的預測內容。字詞預測支援包括[[英文|英文]]、[[中文|中文]]、[[日文|日文]]等14種語言<ref name=":0" /><ref name=":10">{{cite web|url=https://www.cnet.com/how-to/using-ios-8s-quicktype-keyboard/|title=Using iOS 8's QuickType keyboard|accessdate=2016-12-23|date=2014-09-19|last=Cipriani|first=Jason|publisher=[[CBS_Interactive|CBS Interactive]]|website=[[CNET|CNET]]|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20161223201927/https://www.cnet.com/how-to/using-ios-8s-quicktype-keyboard/|archive-date=2016-12-23|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.macworld.co.uk/how-to/iphone/using-quicktype-swype-in-ios-8-3534355/|title=How to use keyboards in iOS 8|accessdate=2016-12-23|date=2014-09-03|last=Hattersley|first=Lucy|publisher=[[International_Data_Group|International Data Group]]|website=[[Macworld|Macworld]]|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20161224030442/http://www.macworld.co.uk/how-to/iphone/using-quicktype-swype-in-ios-8-3534355/|archive-date=2016-12-24|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

iOS 8首度支援第三方输入法，如[[嘸蝦米輸入法|嘸蝦米輸入法]]和[[百度手機輸入法|百度输入法]]等<ref name=":0" /><ref name=":10" /><ref name=":11">{{cite web|url=https://www.forbes.com/sites/gordonkelly/2014/09/22/ios-8-the-best-apple-keyboard-replacements/|title=iOS 8: The Best Apple Keyboard Replacements|accessdate=2016-12-23|date=2014-09-22|last=Kelly|first=Gordon|website=[[Forbes|Forbes]]|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20161223205005/http://www.forbes.com/sites/gordonkelly/2014/09/22/ios-8-the-best-apple-keyboard-replacements/|archive-date=2016-12-23|dead-url=no}}</ref>。在一般情況下，iOS 8皆讓第三方输入法於[[沙盒_(電腦安全)|沙盒]]隔離環境中運作，以免侵害個人隱私。只有用戶選擇開放個人資訊時，输入法才得以收集用戶資料<ref name=":0" /><ref name=":11" />。此外，第三方输入法不支援Siri聽寫功能<ref>{{cite web|url=https://techcrunch.com/2014/10/04/everything-you-need-to-know-about-ios-8-keyboard-permissions-but-were-afraid-to-ask/|title=Everything You Need To Know About iOS 8 Keyboard Permissions (But Were Afraid To Ask)|accessdate=2016-12-23|date=2014-10-04|last=Lomas|first=Natasha|publisher=[[AOL|AOL]]|website=[[TechCrunch|TechCrunch]]|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20161223201827/https://techcrunch.com/2014/10/04/everything-you-need-to-know-about-ios-8-keyboard-permissions-but-were-afraid-to-ask/|archive-date=2016-12-23|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

