iOS 8首度引入家人共享功能，只要共同使用iOS 8和[[OS_X_Yosemite|OS X Yosemite]]以上版本系统的裝置，用户可以與最多6名家庭成员共同分享使用同一张[[信用卡|信用卡]]购买的應用程式、[[音乐|音乐]]及[[电子书|电子书]]等數位內容，不需輸入個別的帳號及密碼<ref name=":9" /><ref>{{Cite news|url=https://support.apple.com/zh-tw/HT201088|title=設定「家人共享」|newspaper=Apple Support|accessdate=2018-08-01|language=zh-TW|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180518201043/https://support.apple.com/zh-tw/HT201088|archive-date=2018-05-18|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{Cite news|url=https://www.kocpc.com.tw/archives/10894|title=iOS 8 家人共享設定完全教學：共用購買App 與信用卡 - 電腦王阿達|date=2014-11-04|newspaper=電腦王阿達|accessdate=2018-08-01|language=zh-TW|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180726122224/https://www.kocpc.com.tw/archives/10894|archive-date=2018-07-26|dead-url=no}}</ref>。不過，未成年成員無法看見成人購買的內容<ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.forbes.com/sites/anthonykosner/2014/06/14/apples-new-family-plan-makes-it-easy-to-solve-the-itunes-identity-crisis/|title=Apple's New Family Plan Makes It Easy To Solve The iTunes Identity Crisis|accessdate=2016-12-26|date=2014-06-14|last=Kosner|first=Andrew|website=[[Forbes|Forbes]]|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20161110093918/http://www.forbes.com/sites/anthonykosner/2014/06/14/apples-new-family-plan-makes-it-easy-to-solve-the-itunes-identity-crisis/|archive-date=2016-11-10|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

家人共享功能也延伸至內建應用程式中，例如为所有家庭成员自动建立的相片串流，及自動同步的[[行事曆_(應用程式)|行事历]]等<ref name=":9" /><ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.apple.com/icloud/family-sharing/|title=Family Sharing. Bring harmony to your family’s digital life.|accessdate=2016-12-26|publisher=[[Apple_Inc.|Apple Inc.]]|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20161228085926/http://www.apple.com/icloud/family-sharing/|archive-date=2016-12-28|dead-url=no}}</ref>。未成年成員也可以藉由[[App_Store_(iOS)|App Store]]、[[iTunes_Store|iTunes Store]]等商店介面向家长传送购买请求<ref name=":9" /><ref>{{cite web|url=https://support.apple.com/en-us/HT201089|title=Request and make purchases with Ask to Buy|accessdate=2016-12-26|publisher=[[Apple_Inc.|Apple Inc.]]|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20161226145100/https://support.apple.com/en-us/HT201089|archive-date=2016-12-26|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

