在iOS 8中，蘋果以「最近加入」標籤取代了「相機膠卷」，但是由於遭到大批用戶及開發者抱怨使用困難，因此蘋果於iOS 8.1更新中加回了標籤<ref>{{Cite news|url=https://chinese.engadget.com/2014/10/02/apple-ios-8-camera-roll/|title=Apple 可能會為 iOS 8 補回「相機膠卷」|newspaper=Engadget 中文版|accessdate=2018-08-01|language=zh-TW|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20161011191104/http://chinese.engadget.com/2014/10/02/apple-ios-8-camera-roll/|archive-date=2016-10-11|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{Cite news|url=https://qooah.com/2014/10/05/camera-roll-is-back-on-ios-8-1/|title=被消失的 Camera Roll 相片膠卷 在 iOS 8.1 上回來了～ - Qooah|newspaper=Qooah|accessdate=2018-08-01|language=zh-TW|archive-date=2018-08-02|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180802042435/https://qooah.com/2014/10/05/camera-roll-is-back-on-ios-8-1/|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{Cite web|url=http://bgr.com/2014/09/23/ios-8-camera-roll/|title=This might just be the most annoying new feature in iOS 8|date=2014-09-23|last=Smith|first=Chris|website=BGR|access-date=2017-01-13|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170116151047/http://bgr.com/2014/09/23/ios-8-camera-roll/|archive-date=2017-01-16|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.cnet.com/news/apple-to-bring-back-camera-roll-with-ios-8-1/|title=Miss the camera roll? Apple iOS 8.1 to bring it back|accessdate=2017-01-08|date=2014-10-16|publisher=[[CBS_Interactive|CBS Interactive]]|first1=Dara|last1=Kerr|first2=Shara|last2=Tibken|website=[[CNET|CNET]]|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170104234728/https://www.cnet.com/news/apple-to-bring-back-camera-roll-with-ios-8-1/|archive-date=2017-01-04|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.businessinsider.com/iphone-users-freaking-out-after-apple-removed-camera-roll-2014-9|title=iPhone Users Are Freaking Out After Apple Removed 'Camera Roll' And Made It Harder To Delete Photos|accessdate=2017-01-08|date=2014-09-22|last=Cook|first=James|publisher=[[Axel_Springer_SE|Axel Springer SE]]|website=[[Business_Insider|Business Insider]]|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170105083149/http://www.businessinsider.com/iphone-users-freaking-out-after-apple-removed-camera-roll-2014-9|archive-date=2017-01-05|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

