===iCloud Drive===
{{Main|iCloud}}
iCloud Drive是苹果提供的[[雲端硬碟|雲端硬碟]]服务。这项新功能允许用户透過[[iCloud|iCloud]]用戶端應用程式及網站，跨平台存取相片、影片、文件及音乐等數位內容<ref>{{Cite web|url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150617082043/http://www.apple.com/tw/ios/whats-new/icloud-drive/|title=Apple - iOS 8 - iCloud Drive|accessdate=2018-08-01|date=2015-06-17}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.techrepublic.com/article/pro-tip-how-to-use-icloud-drive-in-ios-8/|title=Pro tip: How to use iCloud Drive in iOS 8|accessdate=2016-12-26|date=2014-10-22|last=Bohon|first=Cory|publisher=[[CBS_Interactive|CBS Interactive]]|website=[[TechRepublic|TechRepublic]]|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20161226145608/http://www.techrepublic.com/article/pro-tip-how-to-use-icloud-drive-in-ios-8/|archive-date=2016-12-26|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

=== App Store ===
在iOS 8中，App Store介面再度經過重新設計，並推出程式同捆包功能<ref name=":17">{{cite web|url=https://www.macrumors.com/2014/06/02/new-app-store-bundles-betas/|title=Apple to Enhance App Store with 'Explore' Tab, App Bundles, Beta Testing, and More|accessdate=2017-07-20|date=2014-06-02|last=Sumra|first=Husain|website=[[MacRumors|MacRumors]]|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20161004150033/http://www.macrumors.com/2014/06/02/new-app-store-bundles-betas/|archive-date=2016-10-04|dead-url=no}}</ref>。另外，開發者可在應用程式頁面之「預覽」欄位內置入宣傳影片<ref name=":17" />。

===健康===
iOS 8首次引入健康應用程式，详细记录用户的足迹，含氧量、睡眠状态和其他与身体健康有关的数据，還可以整合第三方健康相關應用程式資料<ref>{{Cite web|url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150617223046/http://www.apple.com:80/tw/ios/whats-new/health/|title=Apple - iOS 8 - 健康|accessdate=2018-08-01|date=2015-06-17}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.cnet.com/how-to/apple-health-app-how-to-set-up-import/|title=The complete guide to the iPhone's Health app|accessdate=2016-12-26|date=2014-10-13|last=Profis|first=Sharon|publisher=[[CBS_Interactive|CBS Interactive]]|website=[[CNET|CNET]]|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20161226145322/https://www.cnet.com/how-to/apple-health-app-how-to-set-up-import/|archive-date=2016-12-26|dead-url=no}}</ref>。蘋果也新增了HealthKit及Researchkit[[軟體框架|軟體框架]]，提供开发者开发与新的健康管理应用相整合的软件<ref>{{Cite web|url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150623182859/http://www.apple.com/tw/Researchkit|title=Apple - ResearchKit|accessdate=2018-08-01|date=2015-06-23}}</ref>。

=== HomeKit ===
iOS 8首次引入HomeKit[[軟體框架|軟體框架]]，供開發者開發與控制[[物联网|物聯網]]裝置相關軟體<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.imore.com/homekit-ios-8-explained|title=HomeKit in iOS 8: Explained|accessdate=2016-12-26|date=2014-08-27|last=Ritchie|first=Rene|website=[[iMore|iMore]]|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20161226145924/http://www.imore.com/homekit-ios-8-explained|archive-date=2016-12-26|dead-url=no}}</ref>。任何物聯網裝置想取得HomeKit支援都必須先通過蘋果的認證<ref>{{cite web|url=https://developer.apple.com/homekit/|title=Working with HomeKit|accessdate=2016-12-26|publisher=[[Apple_Inc.|Apple Inc.]]|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170105043219/https://developer.apple.com/homekit/|archive-date=2017-01-05|dead-url=no}}</ref>，並在硬體內加入加密的協同處理器以保護用戶資料<ref>{{cite web|url=http://fortune.com/2015/06/09/ceo-apple-homekit-mess/|title=What one startup CEO learned from handling Apple’s HomeKit mess|accessdate=2016-12-26|date=2015-06-10|last=Higginbotham|first=Stacey|publisher=[[Time_Inc.|Time Inc.]]|website=[[Fortune_(magazine)|Fortune]]|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170202111815/http://fortune.com/2015/06/09/ceo-apple-homekit-mess/|archive-date=2017-02-02|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.theverge.com/2015/1/8/7510647/first-homekit-devices-confirm-apple-tvs-role-in-home-automation|title=First HomeKit devices confirm Apple TV's limited role in home automation|accessdate=2016-12-26|date=2015-01-08|publisher=[[Vox_Media|Vox Media]]|first1=Thomas|last1=Ricker|first2=Jacob|last2=Kastrenakes|website=[[The_Verge|The Verge]]|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20161222082055/http://www.theverge.com/2015/1/8/7510647/first-homekit-devices-confirm-apple-tvs-role-in-home-automation|archive-date=2016-12-22|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

在[[iOS_10|iOS 10]]中，與HomeKit相關的功能整合為家庭應用程式<ref>{{Cite news|url=https://9to5mac.com/2016/09/23/ios-10-how-to-use-new-home-app-control-homekit-devices-video/|title=iOS 10: How to use the new Home app to control HomeKit devices [Video]|date=2016-09-23|newspaper=9to5Mac|accessdate=2018-08-01|language=en-US|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180725110920/https://9to5mac.com/2016/09/23/ios-10-how-to-use-new-home-app-control-homekit-devices-video/|archive-date=2018-07-25|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

=== 音樂 ===
自iOS 8.4起，音樂應用程式內新增了音樂串流服務[[Apple_Music|Apple Music]]及廣播電台[[Beats_1|Beats 1]]<ref>{{cite web|title=Introducing Apple Music — All The Ways You Love Music. All in One Place.|url=https://www.apple.com/pr/library/2015/06/08Introducing-Apple-Music-All-The-Ways-You-Love-Music-All-in-One-Place-.html|publisher=[[Apple_Inc.|Apple Inc.]]|accessdate=2015-07-18|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150729105028/http://www.apple.com/pr/library/2015/06/08Introducing-Apple-Music-All-The-Ways-You-Love-Music-All-in-One-Place-.html|archive-date=2015-07-29|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

=== Passbook ===
{{See Also|Apple Pay}}
自iOS 8.1起，Passbook應用程式加入了對蘋果行動支付服務[[Apple_Pay|Apple Pay]]的支援。Apple Pay僅支援[[iPhone_6|iPhone 6]]及[[iPhone_6_Plus|iPhone 6 Plus]]以上裝置<ref>{{cite web|url=http://appleinsider.com/articles/14/10/20/how-to-set-up-apple-pay-on-an-iphone-6-or-6-plus-running-ios-81-and-where-you-can-use-it-right-now|title=How to set up Apple Pay on an iPhone 6 or 6 Plus running iOS 8.1, and where you can use it right now|accessdate=2016-12-29|date=2014-10-20|last=Hughes|first=Neil|website=AppleInsider|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20161229171930/http://appleinsider.com/articles/14/10/20/how-to-set-up-apple-pay-on-an-iphone-6-or-6-plus-running-ios-81-and-where-you-can-use-it-right-now|archive-date=2016-12-29|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

=== Safari ===
{{Main|Safari}}Safari現在支援[[WebGL|WebGL]]圖形[[應用程式介面|應用程式介面]]<ref>{{cite web|url=https://arstechnica.com/apple/2014/09/ios-8-thoroughly-reviewed/7/|title=iOS 8, thoroughly reviewed|accessdate=2016-12-24|date=2014-09-17|last=Cunningham|first=Andrew|publisher=[[Condé_Nast|Condé Nast]]|website=[[Ars_Technica|Ars Technica]]|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20161112074255/http://arstechnica.com/apple/2014/09/ios-8-thoroughly-reviewed/7/|archive-date=2016-11-12|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

=== 天氣 ===
在iOS 8中，天氣資料來源由[[雅虎|雅虎天氣]]改為[[The_Weather_Channel|The Weather Channel]]<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.recode.net/2014/6/20/11628186/as-weather-channel-blows-yahoo-off-apples-upcoming-ios-8-app-storms|title=As Weather Channel Blows Yahoo Off Apple's Upcoming iOS 8, App Storms Ahead for Mayer|accessdate=2017-01-08|date=2014-06-20|last=Swisher|first=Kara|publisher=[[Vox_Media|Vox Media]]|website=[[Recode|Recode]]|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170109183844/http://www.recode.net/2014/6/20/11628186/as-weather-channel-blows-yahoo-off-apples-upcoming-ios-8-app-storms|archive-date=2017-01-09|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|url=https://9to5mac.com/2014/06/20/why-apple-switched-from-yahoo-to-weather-channel-for-weather-data-in-ios-8/|title=Why Apple switched from Yahoo to Weather Channel for Weather data in iOS 8|accessdate=2017-01-08|date=2014-06-20|last=Kahn|first=Jordan|website=9to5Mac|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170106011236/https://9to5mac.com/2014/06/20/why-apple-switched-from-yahoo-to-weather-channel-for-weather-data-in-ios-8/|archive-date=2017-01-06|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.macrumors.com/2014/06/03/ios-8-new-weather-app/|title=iOS 8 Ditches Yahoo Weather for Content From The Weather Channel|accessdate=2017-02-19|date=2014-06-03|last=Clover|first=Juli|website=[[MacRumors|MacRumors]]|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170220092351/https://www.macrumors.com/2014/06/03/ios-8-new-weather-app/|archive-date=2017-02-20|dead-url=no}}</ref>；同時，應用程式介面也有些許改變<ref>{{cite web|url=http://appleinsider.com/articles/14/06/20/weather-channel-providing-apple-more-detailed-data-for-ios-8-weather-app-than-yahoo-did|title=Weather Channel providing Apple more detailed data for iOS 8 Weather app than Yahoo did|accessdate=2017-01-08|date=2014-06-20|last=Hughes|first=Neil|website=AppleInsider|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170106011359/http://appleinsider.com/articles/14/06/20/weather-channel-providing-apple-more-detailed-data-for-ios-8-weather-app-than-yahoo-did|archive-date=2017-01-06|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

=== Touch ID ===
iOS 8現在允許第三方應用程式使用[[Touch_ID|Touch ID]]<ref>{{cite web|url=http://appleinsider.com/articles/14/09/17/apple-opens-touch-id-to-third-party-applications-with-ios-8|title=Apple opens Touch ID to third-party applications with iOS 8|accessdate=2017-02-18|date=2014-09-17|last=Hughes|first=Neil|website=AppleInsider|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170219112010/http://appleinsider.com/articles/14/09/17/apple-opens-touch-id-to-third-party-applications-with-ios-8|archive-date=2017-02-19|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

