iOS 8新增提示應用程式，定期提供關於[[iOS|iOS]]的小知識<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.macrumors.com/2014/07/21/ios-8-beta-4-tidbits/|title=iOS 8 Beta 4 Tidbits: Tips App, Control Center Redesign, New Display Options|accessdate=2017-01-08|date=2014-07-21|last=Clover|first=Juli|website=[[MacRumors|MacRumors]]|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170108002015/http://www.macrumors.com/2014/07/21/ios-8-beta-4-tidbits/|archive-date=2017-01-08|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

