iOS 8的第二曆法中新增了[[農曆|農曆]]，改善了[[大陸地區|大陸地區]]的地圖資料<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://versus.com/en/2014/06/03/apple-is-out-of-ideas-with-ios8 |title=存档副本 |access-date=2014-06-04 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140603225633/http://versus.com/en/2014/06/03/apple-is-out-of-ideas-with-ios8 |archive-date=2014-06-03 |dead-url=no }}</ref>，同時加強了[[Siri|Siri]]的中文語音識別能力<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://www.eprice.com.hk/mobile/talk/4544/177545/1/ |title=10 個 Apple 沒有告訴你的 iOS 8 功能 |access-date=2014-06-04 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140606184348/http://www.eprice.com.hk/mobile/talk/4544/177545/1 |archive-date=2014-06-06 |dead-url=no }}</ref>。此外，系統語言亦加入了[[香港|香港]]繁體中文的選項<ref name=":13" />。

==問題==

=== iOS 8.0.1更新問題 ===
iOS 8.0.1於2014年9月24日發布。此更新預計將修復如[[HealthKit|HealthKit]]健康功能、第三方鍵盤支援失效、[[簡訊|SMS]]和[[多媒體短訊|MMS]]訊息接收失敗等問題，卻在推出正式版後出現無法接收電信訊號、[[Touch_ID|Touch ID]]失效等問題，蘋果因此緊急撤回更新，並建議受到影響的用戶重新安裝iOS 8.0，等待更新<ref name=":14" /><ref name="8.0.1 broke - The Verge" /><ref name="8.0.1 broke - Engadget" /><ref name="8.0.1 broke - Ars Technica" /><ref name=":15" />。隔日，蘋果推出iOS 8.0.2更新，修正問題<ref name=":2" /><ref name="8.0.2" />。

=== 「Effective power」漏洞 ===
2015年5月，大量iOS 8裝置因為接收到一連串特殊符號及[[阿拉伯语|阿拉伯文]]的通知而[[當機|當機]]重啟<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.macrumors.com/2015/05/26/ios-bug-crashing-iphones-with-text-message/|title=New iOS Bug Crashing iPhones Simply by Receiving a Text Message [Includes Fix]|accessdate=2016-12-27|date=2015-05-26|last=Clover|first=Juli|website=[[MacRumors|MacRumors]]|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170102180610/http://www.macrumors.com/2015/05/26/ios-bug-crashing-iphones-with-text-message/|archive-date=2017-01-02|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.techradar.com/news/phone-and-communications/mobile-phones/this-single-text-message-is-crashing-people-s-iphones-here-s-the-fix-1295019|title=This single text message is crashing people's iPhones - here's the fix|accessdate=2016-12-27|date=2015-05-27|last=Peckham|first=James|publisher=[[Future_plc|Future plc]]|website=[[TechRadar|TechRadar]]|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20161125142204/http://www.techradar.com/news/phone-and-communications/mobile-phones/this-single-text-message-is-crashing-people-s-iphones-here-s-the-fix-1295019|archive-date=2016-11-25|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|url=https://9to5mac.com/2015/05/26/ios-messages-crash-bug/|title=iOS bug causes Messages to crash, iPhone to reboot when a certain text is received|accessdate=2016-12-27|date=2015-05-26|last=Miller|first=Chance|website=9to5Mac|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20161227201225/https://9to5mac.com/2015/05/26/ios-messages-crash-bug/|archive-date=2016-12-27|dead-url=no}}</ref>，若通知持續在鎖定畫面顯示，將導致裝置不斷當機重啟<ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.forbes.com/sites/amitchowdhry/2015/05/27/new-apple-ios-bug-causes-reboots-and-messages-app-crashes|title=New Apple iOS Bug Causes Shut Downs And App Crashes, But There Is A Fix|accessdate=2016-12-27|date=2015-05-27|last=Chowdhry|first=Amit|website=[[Forbes|Forbes]]|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20161228040330/http://www.forbes.com/sites/amitchowdhry/2015/05/27/new-apple-ios-bug-causes-reboots-and-messages-app-crashes/|archive-date=2016-12-28|dead-url=no}}</ref>。此漏洞被媒體稱為「Effective power」。

蘋果於6月底推出iOS 8.4更新，修復了此問題<ref>{{Cite news|url=https://support.apple.com/zh-tw/HT204941|title=關於 iOS 8.4 的安全性內容|newspaper=Apple Support|accessdate=2018-08-01|language=zh-TW|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180219152411/https://support.apple.com/zh-tw/HT204941|archive-date=2018-02-19|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|url=https://arstechnica.com/apple/2015/06/apple-releases-ios-8-4-with-new-music-app-fix-for-crashing-bug/|title=Apple releases iOS 8.4 with new Music app, fix for crashing bug|accessdate=2016-12-27|date=2015-06-30|last=Cunningham|first=Andrew|publisher=[[Condé_Nast|Condé Nast]]|website=[[Ars_Technica|Ars Technica]]|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20161219001541/http://arstechnica.com/apple/2015/06/apple-releases-ios-8-4-with-new-music-app-fix-for-crashing-bug/|archive-date=2016-12-19|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

